has torn
from my agonized heart every earthly good:
but to proceedThe day before I called on
you and
bespoke
the linen for my
sister
Eleanor
,
I had received a note from Mrs.
Ramsay
informing me that a particular relation
was come to town, and as they were
unacquainted
