, and leaving this
house
accompany
me wherever I
choose
to go, I
will to-morrow follow you to the Church
and in the face of the whole congregation
expose
your infamous conduct, and claim my
prior right not only to your
person
, but to
all the wealth your infatuated lover has
heaped
upon you.What were my
sufferings
at this horrid moment. Turn either way,
infamy
stared
me in the face. I was unable
to determine what plan to
pursue
. To
remain
in London was
impossible
, after what
had
past
as I
should
undoubtedly have been
the
jest
even of my own
