and goes to Clara, where
ruin and infamy, I fear, will
soon
overtake
her. I
shall
write no more on this
side
the
channel. Heaven grant that Kingly may
recover, and
Rooksby
awaken to a
sense
of
his errors. Then may the pale
messenger
of
peace beckon me from this vale of
sorrow
to
that
blessed
mansion
, where the tear
shall
cease
to
slow
, and the heart be
eased
of its
anguish
.
MERIEL.
